Look at your mother.

6
00:01:20,560 --> 00:01:21,840
Do you miss her?

7
00:01:23,080 --> 00:01:25,320
Her death anniversary is coming soon.

8
00:01:26,920 --> 00:01:28,320
Take that step.

9
00:01:29,160 --> 00:01:30,680
Just like your mother did.

10
00:01:32,720 --> 00:01:33,880
Just one step.

11
00:01:34,520 --> 00:01:36,640
You'll see her soon.

12
00:01:49,080 --> 00:01:51,280
I knew about my dad's illegal card room.

13
00:01:51,880 --> 00:01:54,440
And that my mom was paying off his debts.

14
00:01:55,759 --> 00:01:56,800
I also knew

15
00:01:57,720 --> 00:01:59,520
my father's public humiliation

16
00:01:59,640 --> 00:02:01,640
was the last straw for my mother.

17
00:02:03,080 --> 00:02:04,610
Otherwise, how do you think

18
00:02:05,040 --> 00:02:06,900
Xu Xiaodao was caught so quickly?

19
00:02:07,360 --> 00:02:09,520
If Liang Ruqing hadn't used tutoring as an excuse

20
00:02:09,520 --> 00:02:11,050
to interfere in our family,

21
00:02:11,680 --> 00:02:13,740
my mother, even if living miserably,

22
00:02:13,840 --> 00:02:15,500
wouldn't have chosen to jump.

23
00:02:15,960 --> 00:02:17,920
My mother and I wouldn't be separated by death.

24
00:02:17,920 --> 00:02:19,180
So she deserves to die.

25
00:02:22,400 --> 00:02:23,660
But you don't know that

26
00:02:24,120 --> 00:02:26,520
the last text your mother sent before she died

27
00:02:26,520 --> 00:02:27,880
was to Teacher Liang.

28
00:02:29,160 --> 00:02:30,200
Thanking her.

29
00:02:37,840 --> 00:02:38,640
This

30
00:02:39,800 --> 00:02:42,060
is what we found in Liang Ruqing's phone.

31
00:02:43,520 --> 00:02:44,980
Your mother had attempted

32
00:02:45,000 --> 00:02:46,800
suicide multiple times before.

33
00:02:47,000 --> 00:02:48,880
It was always Liang Ruqing who talked her out of it.

34
00:02:48,880 --> 00:02:50,010
Your tutoring fees -

35
00:02:50,800 --> 00:02:52,640
Liang Ruqing never took a penny.

36
00:02:53,520 --> 00:02:56,000
Even some of the gambling debts your mother paid for your father

37
00:02:56,000 --> 00:02:58,240
came from Liang Ruqing's financial support.

38
00:02:58,240 --> 00:02:59,240
Do you think such a person

39
00:02:59,240 --> 00:03:01,970
would encourage your mother to jump to her death?

40
00:03:04,360 --> 00:03:05,360
Just now on the rooftop,

41
00:03:05,360 --> 00:03:07,220
I think you've already realized.

42
00:03:07,320 --> 00:03:09,200
Actually, you and Liang Ruqing are the same -

43
00:03:09,200 --> 00:03:12,640
both implanted with the psychological anchor to commit suicide afterward.

44
00:03:12,640 --> 00:03:13,440
Xu Yang.

45
00:03:15,480 --> 00:03:16,740
You're a smart person.

46
00:03:16,880 --> 00:03:19,560
The person who manipulated you will never let you go.

47
00:03:19,560 --> 00:03:22,000
So there's only one path ahead of you now.

48
00:03:22,280 --> 00:03:24,160
Tell the police the truth.

49
00:03:24,400 --> 00:03:27,060
Help catch the person who dragged you into this.

50
00:03:27,280 --> 00:03:30,920
This way you can also atone for wrongfully killing Liang Ruqing.

51
00:03:31,800 --> 00:03:32,920
And I believe

52
00:03:34,040 --> 00:03:34,920
your mother

53
00:03:35,560 --> 00:03:37,760
would certainly want to see you do this.

54
00:03:39,160 --> 00:03:40,760
After my mother passed away,

55
00:03:41,360 --> 00:03:43,280
I felt like I lost my soul.

56
00:03:43,480 --> 00:03:45,600
I couldn't get out of my grief at all.

57
00:03:46,240 --> 00:03:48,440
My classmates saw my social media posts

58
00:03:49,520 --> 00:03:51,240
