59
00:03:51,240 --> 00:03:52,720
You should really see a therapist.

60
00:03:52,720 --> 00:03:54,240
I hate the way they talk.

61
00:03:54,760 --> 00:03:56,200
They've never lost a mother.

62
00:03:56,200 --> 00:03:57,680
They can't possibly understand how I feel.

63
00:03:57,680 --> 00:03:58,160
Xu Yang.

64
00:04:01,200 --> 00:04:02,860
I don't have a mental illness.

65
00:04:03,360 --> 00:04:04,720
I just can't accept

66
00:04:05,680 --> 00:04:07,880
the reality that my mother passed away.

67
00:04:09,640 --> 00:04:10,570
A few months ago.

68
00:04:11,280 --> 00:04:13,280
I met this female doctor named Hu Li.

69
00:04:32,720 --> 00:04:34,040
What else do you know

70
00:04:34,560 --> 00:04:35,720
about this female doctor?

71
00:04:35,720 --> 00:04:37,040
She always wore a mask

72
00:04:38,080 --> 00:04:40,720
or large sunglasses.

73
00:04:40,720 --> 00:04:41,880
Even during hypnosis,

74
00:04:41,880 --> 00:04:42,840
when she took off her mask,

75
00:04:42,840 --> 00:04:44,700
I couldn't make out her true face.

76
00:04:45,159 --> 00:04:46,290
But she was sincere,

77
00:04:46,720 --> 00:04:47,850
understood me well,

78
00:04:48,240 --> 00:04:50,170
and could always read my thoughts.

79
00:04:51,240 --> 00:04:52,960
She said she's a psychiatrist

80
00:04:53,480 --> 00:04:56,080
and asked me to help her with a therapy project.

81
00:04:57,159 --> 00:04:57,960
Hu Li.

82
00:04:58,240 --> 00:05:02,040
She's the only attending physician in the psychiatric department.

83
00:05:05,120 --> 00:05:05,920
Go on.

84
00:05:06,320 --> 00:05:07,560
The important thing is

85
00:05:07,560 --> 00:05:09,400
she doesn't lecture me like everyone else

86
00:05:09,400 --> 00:05:10,920
telling me to move on with my life.

87
00:05:10,920 --> 00:05:13,380
Do you remember what your mother looks like?

88
00:05:15,520 --> 00:05:16,920
Now close your eyes.

89
00:05:17,320 --> 00:05:18,720
I'll take you to find her.

90
00:05:21,200 --> 00:05:22,600
She misses you very much.

91
00:05:25,320 --> 00:05:26,800
She helps me see the memories

92
00:05:26,800 --> 00:05:28,400
of daily life with my mother.

93
00:05:28,800 --> 00:05:30,060
That's why I trust her.

94
00:05:31,200 --> 00:05:32,530
And I'm grateful to her.

95
00:05:36,280 --> 00:05:38,840
Your mother was manipulated into committing suicide.

96
00:05:38,840 --> 00:05:40,440
Don't you want to avenge her?

97
00:05:42,120 --> 00:05:44,159
The learning atmosphere at the technical school is unstable.

98
00:05:44,159 --> 00:05:46,880
Dr. Hu told me to pretend to be studious

99
00:05:47,400 --> 00:05:49,530
to attract Liang Ruqing's attention.

100
00:05:50,000 --> 00:05:50,930
Thank you, Miss.

101
00:05:51,920 --> 00:05:52,640
Xu Yang.

102
00:05:57,960 --> 00:05:59,560
I've been wanting to talk to you,

103
00:05:59,560 --> 00:06:01,620
