104
00:06:01,920 --> 00:06:03,520
I'm glad to see you're moving on.

105
00:06:03,520 --> 00:06:04,640
It makes me happy.

106
00:06:07,520 --> 00:06:08,080
Miss,

107
00:06:08,080 --> 00:06:09,520
I'm actually fine.

108
00:06:10,360 --> 00:06:13,020
