118
00:06:30,840 --> 00:06:32,500
You might want to give it a try.

119
00:06:32,760 --> 00:06:33,560
Okay.

120
00:06:33,800 --> 00:06:34,600
Thank you.

121
00:06:35,280 --> 00:06:36,340
Goodbye, teacher.

122
00:06:42,600 --> 00:06:43,400
So,

123
00:06:43,840 --> 00:06:46,240
the doctor you recommended to Liang Ruqing

124
00:06:46,520 --> 00:06:47,780
is this female doctor?

125
00:06:50,000 --> 00:06:51,200
How many times did she go?

126
00:06:51,200 --> 00:06:52,200
I don't know.

127
00:06:52,360 --> 00:06:53,520
Did you go with her?

128
00:06:53,680 --> 00:06:55,680
I went with her the first few times,

129
00:06:56,480 --> 00:06:58,140
