148
00:07:49,920 --> 00:07:51,840
I did some research.

149
00:07:52,240 --> 00:07:54,240
Compared to other popular players,

150
00:07:54,280 --> 00:07:56,340
he has almost no fans in this country.

151
00:07:56,520 --> 00:07:58,000
And your classmate mentioned

152
00:07:58,000 --> 00:07:59,040
that you used to wear

153
00:07:59,040 --> 00:08:00,480
Kobe's number 24 jersey.

154
00:08:00,760 --> 00:08:02,420
