155
00:08:02,880 --> 00:08:04,280
Hu Li told me to change it.

156
00:08:04,760 --> 00:08:06,040
She didn't tell me why.

157
00:08:07,000 --> 00:08:08,120
I'm curious too.

158
00:08:08,960 --> 00:08:11,080
What does this have to do with hypnosis?

159
00:08:11,080 --> 00:08:11,880
Xu Yang.

160
00:08:12,920 --> 00:08:14,920
You're too clever for your own good.

161
00:08:15,400 --> 00:08:17,530
At the moment Liang Ruqing was killed,

162
00:08:17,800 --> 00:08:19,000
you had already figured out

163
00:08:19,000 --> 00:08:21,000
how to clear yourself of suspicion.

164
00:08:21,040 --> 00:08:22,160
Did you think

165
00:08:22,160 --> 00:08:25,360
