177
00:08:43,600 --> 00:08:45,600
She said the less I knew, the better.

178
00:08:45,840 --> 00:08:47,440
Even if the police caught me,

179
00:08:48,200 --> 00:08:49,660
they couldn't convict me.

180
00:08:50,040 --> 00:08:50,680
Just like my mother

181
00:08:50,680 --> 00:08:52,410
who was killed by Liang Ruqing.

182
00:08:53,400 --> 00:08:56,440
