242
00:11:00,560 --> 00:11:01,840
Xu Yang's mother has passed away,

243
00:11:01,840 --> 00:11:03,560
and his father is suspected of a crime.

244
00:11:03,560 --> 00:11:04,640
I've already spoken with the

245
00:11:04,640 --> 00:11:06,080
